So it gives us a little hint as to how, as to the path that we're actually moving on when we practice meditation and in daily life.

185
00:26:02,655 --> 00:26:07,161
So he made no distinction whatsoever between samsara and nibbana.

186
00:26:07,580 --> 00:26:13,467
It was all to do with relationship.

187
00:26:13,487 --> 00:26:28,883
So I can only hope a revision of the six realms will be an occasion for you to really work on your practice, etc., etc., and be liberated in no time at all.

188
00:26:29,644 --> 00:26:30,384
Peace and joy.

